                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-5829&quot; title=&quot;too many EXPORT_SYMBOL in code&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-5829&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-5829&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; removed a lot of EXPORT_SYMBOL, including for the lu_ref_* functions. As these functions are only compiled in when the --enable-lu_ref is passed to configure, the breakage was missed.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
